受疫情影响，希尔顿关停中国150家酒店。
Affected by the outbreak, Hilton closed 150 hotels in China.
郑萃颖。
Zheng Guangying.
界面新闻                      。
Interface news.
界面新闻。
Interface news.
界面新闻是中国具有影响力的原创财经新媒体，只服务于独立思考的人群。
Interface News is an original and influential new financial media in China, serving only the people who think independently.
Photo by Serhii Maksymiv on Unsplash记者：郑萃颖“ 在2020年第一季度，预计疫情对调整后税息折旧及摊销前收益的影响在1000万美元至2000万美元。
Photo by Serhii Maksymv on Unsplash: "In the first quarter of 2020, the impact of the epidemic on earnings before adjusted tax depreciation and amortization is expected to be between $10 million and $20 million.
”希尔顿集团近日发布了2019年第四季度及全年财报。
Hilton recently released its fourth quarter 2019 and full-year results.
在发布后的分析会议上，希尔顿集团执行副总裁兼首席财务官Kevin J. Jacobs称，目前已关闭中国地区大约150家希尔顿旗下酒店，共约33000间客房。
In a post-release analysis session, Kevin J. Jacobs, executive vice president and chief financial officer of the Hilton Group, said about 150 Hilton hotels in China, with about 33,000 rooms, have been closed.
他表示，假设疫情需要持续3到6个月，再加上之后3到6个月的恢复期，可能会给希尔顿集团2020全年收益造成2500万美元至5000万美元的损失。
Assuming the outbreak takes three to six months, plus a recovery period of three to six months, he said, it could cost the Hilton Group between $25 million and $50 million in full-year earnings for 2020.
在2020年第一季度，预计疫情对调整后税息折旧及摊销前收益的影响在1000万美元至2000万美元。
In the first quarter of 2020, the impact of the epidemic on earnings before adjusted tax depreciation and amortization is expected to be between $10 million and $20 million.
根据最新财报，2019年第四季度，希尔顿在亚太地区的酒店RevPAR数据同比下降了3.8%，其中中国市场的酒店RevPAR下降了7.8%，原因与休闲旅游热度降温和香港市场有关。
In the fourth quarter of 2019, Hilton's Asia-Pacific hotel RevPAR fell 3.8% YoY, with the Chinese hotel RevPAR down 7.8%, according to the latest results.
2019年全年，中国市场的酒店RevPAR同比下降了3.2%。
For all of 2019, China's hotel RevPAR fell 3.2% year on year.
财报预计，2020年日本奥林匹克运动会的热度能一定程度对冲中国市场疫情带来的影响。
The report predicts the 2020 Games will be hot enough to hedge against an epidemic in China.
希尔顿首席执行官Chris Nassetta表示，在过去一年，希尔顿在全球新签约的酒店中，超过20%位于中国。
Chris Nassetta, Hilton's chief executive, said more than 20 per cent of the new hotels signed up globally in the past year were in China.
由于看好中国市场的发展潜力，希尔顿在中国市场不断加大投入。
Mr Hilton is investing more and more in the Chinese market because he is optimistic about its growth potential.
2019年6月，希尔顿在中国的第200家酒店开业，另有约430家筹建中的酒店。
In June 2019, Hilton opened its 200th hotel in China and has about 430 hotels in the pipeline.
彭博社援引希尔顿酒店集团发言人Nigel Glennie称，部分受影响酒店仍会对已有的订单进行运营，并为紧急人员提供服务。
Bloomberg quoted Hilton Group spokesman Nigel Glennie as saying some of the affected hotels would still be operating existing orders and providing emergency services.
据希尔顿集团官方微信号显示，武汉光谷希尔顿酒店、武汉世贸希尔顿酒店、十堰希尔顿花园酒店，在疫情中承担起为一线医疗队服务的工作。
According to Hilton Group official micro-signal, Wuhan Guanggu Hilton Hotel, Wuhan World Trade Center Hilton Hotel, Shiyan Hilton Garden Hotel, in the outbreak of the work of the first-line medical team.
。
